      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s in absolute pristine condition with zero scratches or wear. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car smell. I'm looking for a great new home for it, and I promise you won\u2019t find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
