    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, presenting in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, positive engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and internal mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering response these analog icons are known for. A pristine, no-excuses specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
