      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been exclusively garage-kept and shielded from the elements, resulting in an exterior finish that is absolutely flawless; the paint retains a deep, liquid-like luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a pristine dashboard that still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every technological feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced strictly at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history provided. With low mileage and a history of being hand-washed only, this is a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands perfection and refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
