      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and it shows in every detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
