    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD3S stands as a benchmark for JDM preservation, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary power plant with its sequential twin-turbocharger system delivering seamless boost transitions. The longitudinal front-midship architecture provides a near-perfect polar moment of inertia, paired with a factory-spec four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential for razor-sharp lateral response. Mechanically superlative, the engine maintains excellent compression across all rotor faces, and the complex vacuum solenoid rack has been professionally validated for total system integrity. With zero chassis fatigue and a flawless undercarriage, this collector-grade specimen offers the precise, unadulterated feedback that defined the golden era of Japanese performance engineering.",
